title: NFL ATL: Week 10 TNF Preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 10 TNF Preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- previews the Week 10 “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Washington Redskins and Minnesota Vikings. The crew discusses what the Aaron Rodgers injury means for the Green Bay Packers and will “Stick a Fork” in one unlucky team. Find out if Wesseling is getting closer to sticking a fork in his softball pants. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL
